-- Tianyi Fruit in Talks to Supply PepsiCo in China, Standard Says
-- Joshua Fellman
-- 2010-09-20T20:07:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/tianyi-fruit-in-initial-talks-to-supply-pepsico-in-china-standard-reports.html

          
          
             Tianyi Fruit Holdings Ltd . is in
preliminary talks to supply  PepsiCo  Inc. with frozen
concentrated fruit juice in China, the Standard said, citing
Chairman Sin Ke.   
 The company has been the sole supplier of the commodity to
 Coca-Cola Co . in China for the past five years, and will consult
with the soft-drink maker before any decision, the Hong Kong-
based English-language newspaper reported today.    
